data.description:
This remarkable 1-owner home is perfectly situated right next to a serene park, providing a picturesque backdrop to your everyday life. The property boasts a sparkling pool set within a fully fenced private backyard, creating an oasis of relaxation and entertainment. With only 7 years of age, this modern gem offers contemporary living at its finest.The main level features a convenient downstairs bedroom with a full-size bathroom, making it ideal for guests or family members who prefer single-level living. With ample space for entertainment, you'll find it easy to host gatherings and create lasting memories.Retreat to the huge master bedroom, a spacious sanctuary that offers comfort and tranquility. The community is served by excellent schools, making it an ideal location! Nestled in the charming community of Greenacres, Florida, 4843 Pond Pine Way is a unique and pristine single-owner home that offers a lifestyle of comfort, convenience, and modern elegance. From its ideal location next to a beautiful park to the delightful features it boasts, this 7-year-old residence presents an inviting opportunity for those seeking the perfect place to call home. 

**Location, Location, Location:** 
One of the standout features of this property is its prime location. Situated right next to a serene park, 4843 Pond Pine Way offers a picturesque view and a feeling of tranquility that's hard to match. Whether you enjoy morning walks, picnics, or simply the beauty of nature, having a park as your neighbor is a true luxury. 

**Outdoor Oasis:** 
As you step into the backyard, you'll be greeted by a fantastic private oasis. The property features a sparkling pool with limestone surrounding, perfect for enjoying those sunny Florida days. The fully fenced backyard not only ensures your privacy but also creates a secure space for both relaxation and recreation. Imagine hosting summer barbecues, family gatherings, or simply lounging by the pool - all within the comfort of your own backyard. 

**Modern Living:** 
Built just seven years ago, this home exudes a contemporary charm. Modern design and architecture are evident throughout, with a layout that's tailored to meet the demands of today's lifestyle. The interior is spacious and thoughtfully designed, ensuring a seamless flow between rooms and providing a wealth of possibilities for customization. 
**Main Level Convenience:** 
One of the highlights of this home is the presence of a downstairs bedroom complete with a full-size bathroom. This feature not only adds an extra layer of convenience but also offers flexible options for accommodating guests, in-laws, or anyone who prefers single-level living. The accessibility of this additional bedroom and bathroom makes daily life more comfortable and accessible. 

**Entertainment Space:** 
For those who love to entertain, this home has it all. With a layout that prioritizes open space, there is plenty of room for social gatherings, parties, and family get-togethers. Whether it's a cozy movie night in the living room, a formal dinner in the dining area, or a casual barbecue on the patio, this home provides a fantastic canvas for creating memories. 

**Master Retreat:** 
The master bedroom in this residence is a sight to behold. Spacious and inviting, it offers the perfect sanctuary at the end of a long day. Whether you're looking for a private space to unwind, read a book, or simply enjoy the comfort of a spacious bedroom, this master suite delivers in style and comfort. Huge walk-in closets for extra storage!

**Top-Notch Education:** 
Families will appreciate the excellent schools in the area, ensuring that your children have access to quality education. With schools nearby, you can have peace of mind knowing that your children are in a supportive and enriching learning environment. 

**Turn-Key Perfection:** 
This home is the epitome of turn-key living. It's ready and waiting for its next owner to move in and start enjoying all the wonderful features it has to offer. The well-maintained property, modern amenities, and a traditional design that's built for today's lifestyle make it an ideal choice for those who want to experience the best of Florida living right from day one. In conclusion, 4843 Pond Pine Way in Greenacres, Florida, is a one-of-a-kind home with a host of features that cater to modern living. From its proximity to the park and a private backyard with a pool to a flexible floor plan, this home offers a lifestyle that's hard to beat. Whether you're looking for a serene retreat, a space to entertain, or a comfortable place for your family to grow, this residence is ready to exceed your expectations. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own and create lasting memories in this remarkable Florida gem.
